 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x109e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此次作战的目的、{00}是迎击联邦的巡逻舰队！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae864ef2fef28e7b4d5e7b40200e7b6e931e7ccef2ed1e7b4ec12ec3fe7d4e7c9060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x10b8",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "发挥演习所学、这种敌人不足为惧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e870e949ea2feab6e7fbeb5502e7b9e7d1e7e3efb2e7b5ea1ee7c1ec6eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x10df",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全员、开战！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e84902e7faef28ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1128",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "按选择键打开『游戏指令』、",
   "zh_hex": "15ea76e966eaaaeb71e7f5e7fa0cea94ea3ee8c0e94e0d020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1144",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "选『胜利条件』、可确认本关胜败条件",
   "zh_hex": "15e9660ce8dbe82ee9d4e9910d02e7c4e88ce8a0d2e8bbe8dbe88fe9d4e991000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1167",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本关的胜利条件是『歼灭全部敌军』",
   "zh_hex": "15d2e8bbe7b4e8dbe82ee9d4e991e7b60ceaafe8e1bbcce7e3e7e00d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x117f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "失败条件则是『德托洛夫被击破』",
   "zh_hex": "15e8a5e88fe9d4e991ea87e7b60ce82ce7f4e94ae830e7f1e7ccef6d0d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1192",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "注意别让德托洛夫的桑吉巴尔被击破、把{00}敌军歼灭吧",
   "zh_hex": "15eaccef3ce7e5e7f9e82ce7f4e94ae830e7b4ea2be7d9e85be7e1e7f1e7ccc702e81b00e7e3e7e0eaafe8e1e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11e8",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "单位受到的伤害、以及打出的弹药……",
   "zh_hex": "15e918e834e8c8e7d7e7b4e8f9e98802e7f3e9cfe7f5efbee7b4e946ebed09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11fe",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要搭载进战舰、就能得到回复",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2aeb09eb1de892ef28e7d402e7c5e7c6e80ae7d7ef52e9ee0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1250",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战舰的舰长、拥有名为『指挥能力』的能{00}力……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7d4e7b4e7d4ef3402eb35e7cbe8ace7c10ce8c0e949e7c6efb00de7b4e7c600efb009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x126d",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "会根据能力等级、在战舰周围施加指挥效{00}果",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e2e9b8e8cce7c6efb0e826eaee02ef29ef28e7d4ea5ce9deeb8de854e8c0e949ea8f00e8710000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1292",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在这指挥效果所及的范围内作战……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b9e8c0e949ea8fe871e7fbe9cfe7b4ec8ee9dee99aef2fef2809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12b2",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "参战的单位、命中与回避都会按能力等级{00}获得加成",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1aef28e7b4e918e83402e853c0e8328ccae840e7e2ea76e7c6dae826eaee00e9d8e80ae854e837000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12d6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "部分『ID指令』会影响整个指挥范围、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef70efae0cef62ef96e8c0e94e0de7e2ea8eecbfe9fee828e8c0e949ec8ee9de020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12fb",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在舰长的指挥范围内作战、便能更有利地{00}推进战斗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7d4ef34e7b4e8c0e949ec8ee9dee99aef2fef2802e8fae7c6e952e7cbe82ebf00eaabe892ef28e7ff000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x133e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "已击退敌军！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3ae7cce880e7e3e7e0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1369",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "干得好！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d3e80ae7c7ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1375",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "照这样下去、往后的战斗也无需担心了",
   "zh_hex": "15ea1ae7b9e7daef4de7eb02e911e7fee7b4ef28e7ffe7c0e7dce92de9fde82de7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x138c",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全员、撤退！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e84902e90ae880ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13b4",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才那一战、不愧是海兵队啊……打得真{00}漂亮",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7b7efb6ef2802e7b5ea08e7b6e91bef93e7c9e7c30909e7f5e80ae82000ead0eaa20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13ea",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您夏亚大佐才是、真不愧是『赤色彗星』{00}啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e835ef37e7d6bea3e836e7b602e820e7b5ea08e7b60ce9e9e89fe9b6b50d00e7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x140a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "照这样子、追击木马应该也不会太难了吧",
   "zh_hex": "15ea1ae7b9e7dae88602e8dde7ccefa9e84fe873e898e7c0e7b5e7e2e86ae866e7bae7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1443",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……木马的战力、远非寻常部队可比",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909d4e84fe7b4ef28da02e94ce8f0efe2b3cce7c9e7c4e825000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x145f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、还是该把准备做得周全才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6d902e7f7e7b6e898e81be87ae877e81ce80aea5cbbe8369f000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1496",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是说……前往SIDE6吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6e7ed0909ef51e911ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cde802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14c0",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽因演习和遭遇联邦军耽搁了些、但本就{00}打算补充战力",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8ef33ea2feab6e7d3eb1eea43ef2eefaae7e0eda7ed6ae7bae8a402e7dbefa6e7c500e7f5e889ea81ea86ef28efb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14e5",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之按原定计划前往SIDE6、与弗拉{00}纳冈机关的新人类们会合",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cdea76e8e4e867ea55ea74ef51e911ef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cd02e832e9b5e7c200e882eb7ee7e4e8bbe7b4ef8aefb2e841e7bbe7e2efc00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1504",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西玛中佐、你也没异议吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e845ef4eefba02e7b8e7c0e7d8eb32e8e3e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1531",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、夏亚大佐的判断、我信得过",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502ef37e7d6efa5efbae7b4eb29e98202efcce90fe80aef360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1554",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "德托洛夫！航向、转往SID{SLOT:4223}6！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82ce7f4e94ae83006e9c19d02e9c2e911141211ef9fe9cd060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x157f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！……明白！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6060909ef39e809060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3a82",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此！夏亚没能击沉木马吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efcfe7f0e7caef97ef37e7d6e7d8e7c6e7cce983efa9e84fe802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ab3",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木马似乎已朝SIDE6方向逃走",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9e84fe944e933ef3aeaadef9eef62ef96ef9fe9cdefb1efc1e8c2e8900000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3ae5",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这可真是天赐良机！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c4e820e7b6e844eff2eaf0e7e4ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3af0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！立刻命舰队出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97e86be91fe853e7d4e7c9efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3b04",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就在夏亚眼皮底下、{00}把木马击沉给他看！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5ef29ef37e7d6e90bebdde9b4890200e81bd4e84fe7cce983e839e80ce7f60606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3bbe",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇、哇啊啊啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea8802ea88e7c3e7c3e7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3bfa",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "德托洛夫！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82ce7f4e94ae830ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3c26",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！旗舰竟被击破……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d090906eb0be7d4ef2ce7f1e7ccc7090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x425e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐！补给部队已经抵达了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6efa5efbaef97ea81e839ef70e7c9ef3ae8b7e96eef2be7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x428f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……补给部队？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea81e839ef70e7c9050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x42ba",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是第300战队的夏亚大佐吧？这是来{00}自格拉纳达的补给物资",
