  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x432e",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……这是来自开发部以及参谋本部的援{00}助",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b9e7b6d9abe7fae870cce7f3e9cfed1aea6ed2cce7b4e86300ea2300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x434c",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是献给将系统图达成100%、且自前{00}作起持续奋战的贵队……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6ec2de839e84ae941e929eb2def2be837eff7e998e998ead902e999efb5ef5100ef2fe847e9efe9adef46ef28e7b4e930e7c909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4373",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是来自这两个部局的一份谢意",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efcfefb5e7b9e97de828ef70ea8ce7b4efb6ea22e8b2ef3c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43a3",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗、那我就心怀感激地收下了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e80202e7b7efcce7c5e82deb03e87de9b9ef63e926ef4de7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43d4",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43da",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "参谋部赠送性能零件2件、以及定制零件{00}8件",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1aea6eccedbae9bae951e7c6eb74e9910fe99102e7f3e9cfe867e8deeb74e99100ec44e99100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x43fc",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
