   "zh_hex": "15e812e7e4ef30eaabe892e8c3ec03e99102e812e951e7c6e83de895cee98fec03e991000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4414",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "共计20件改造零件",
   "zh_hex": "15ea48ea55ef5fe998e991e9f0e93eeb74e9910000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4423",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、开发部赠予全部种类的变换零件、{00}各1件",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7fae870ccedbad6bbcce7d1e841e7b4e955ea78eb74e9910200e8190ee99100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4444",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请把它们用在今后的战局上",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae81be978e7bbefb3ef29efb9e7fee7b4ef28ea8cef4c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4476",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……这是来自参谋本部的援助",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b9e7b6d9abed1aea6ed2cce7b4e863ea23000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x448f",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是本部对自前作起便奋战至今的贵队的{00}一份谢意",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6efa6ef70e7beefb5ef51ef2fe847e8faef46ef28e897efb9e7b4e930e7c9e7b400efb6ea22e8b2ef3c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x44d1",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗、那我就心怀感激地收下了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e80202e7b7efcce7c5e82deb03e87de9b9ef63e926ef4de7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4502",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！那么、清单如下……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97e7b7e7bd02e995e918e7f0ef4d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4511",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "性能零件2件、定制零件8件",
   "zh_hex": "15e951e7c6eb74e991ef5fe99102e867e8deeb74e991ec44e9910000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x452b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高机动推进器5件、高性能光束兵装5件",
   "zh_hex": "15e812e7e4ef30eaabe892e8c3ec03e99102e812e951e7c6e83de895cee98fec03e991000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4543",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请收下合计20件改造零件",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae926ef4defc0ea55ef5fe998e991e9f0e93eeb74e9910000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x457a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……这是来自开发部的援助",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b9e7b6efcfefb5e7fae870ef70e7b4e863ea230000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x4592",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是献给将系统图达成100%、为我军{00}MS开发立下功劳的贵队……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6ec2de839e84ae941e929eb2def2be837eff7e998e998ead902e7c1efcce7e000efa7ef9ee7fae870e86bef4de9b1ec4ae7b4e930e7c909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x45b6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是来自开发部的一份谢意",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efcfefb5e7fae870ef70e7b4efb6ea22e8b2ef3c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x45e4",
